## Scope per version
 
### v1 — MVP (Core booking loop)
*Smallest possible thing to take a real booking and manage it.*
 
**IN:**
- Property listing pages (all properties always visible — no search/filter needed at this scale)
- Instant booking with payment (Stripe, PayPal, manual)
- Automated booking confirmation email (summary + check-in instructions)
- Admin: view, create, edit, cancel bookings
- Admin: iCal / Google Calendar sync for availability
- Admin: add/edit/publish property listings
 
**OUT (deliberately deferred):**
- AI chat assistant → v2
- Guest CRM → v2 (a basic contact log is enough in v1)
- Multilingual → v3
- Any AI agent → v2 or later
- Analytics dashboard → v4
- Reviews → v5
 
---
 
### v2 — Communications (Guest messaging automation)
*Remove the manual messaging burden. Make the guest experience feel professional.*
 
**IN:**
- AI agent: auto-reply to guest inquiries within 60 seconds
- AI agent: pre-arrival message (48h before check-in — instructions, door code, house rules)
- AI agent: post-stay follow-up (24h after check-out)
- AI chat assistant on property pages (guests ask questions, get instant answers)
- Admin: message template editor (review/edit AI templates)
- Admin: guest CRM (contact history, notes, tags)
- All AI messages logged in CRM record
 
---
 
### v3 — Marketing (Content & social automation)
*Organic and paid traffic on autopilot. Platform starts finding its own guests.*
 
**IN:**
- AI agent: blog content suggestion (weekly ideas based on season, trends, occupancy gaps)
- AI agent: blog writing & publishing (approved posts published to CMS in all languages)
- AI agent: SEO content for property pages and landing pages
- AI agent: Facebook/Instagram ad campaigns (triggered by occupancy gaps)
- Multilingual support: English, Swedish, German, Dutch (all guest-facing content)
- Admin: content approval queue (approve/reject AI blog suggestions)
- Admin: ad campaign reporting (reach, clicks, attributed bookings)
 
---
 
### v4 — Intelligence (Revenue optimisation)
*Start making data-driven decisions. The platform earns more per booking automatically.*
 
**IN:**
- AI agent: dynamic pricing (adjust nightly rate by season, demand, local events)
- Admin: floor/ceiling price rules per property
- Admin: analytics dashboard (occupancy rate, revenue, avg nightly rate, traffic sources)
- Admin: revenue report export
- AI pricing change log + admin alerts for large adjustments
 
---
 
### v5 — Scale (Growth & retention)
*Maximise repeat bookings and open backup channels.*
 
**IN:**
- Reviews and ratings (guests leave reviews post-stay)
- OTA channel sync (Airbnb, Booking.com as backup channels)
- Direct messaging thread UI (replace email-only with in-app thread)
- Multi-property discount logic (e.g. book both properties, get 10% off)
- Guest loyalty / repeat booking incentive
 
---
 
### Permanently out of scope (for now)
- Custom-built calendar (use iCal sync instead)
- Mobile app
- Marketplace / multi-host features
 
