## User story format
 
> **[vX] Story title**
>
> **As a** [actor],
> **I want to** [action],
> **So that** [benefit].
>
> **Acceptance criteria:**
> - Criterion 1
> - Criterion 2
> - Criterion 3
>
> *Labels: `[v1]` `[External API]` etc.*
 
